Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
applyGlobalNets(25.10)                                  applyGlobalNets(25.10)

Name
       applyGlobalNets - Applies or restores the global net connectivity rules
       to  the  design and creates the necessary connections between instances
       and these global nets

Syntax
       applyGlobalNets

       [-help]

       Applies or restores the global net connectivity rules to the design and
       creates the necessary connections between instances  and  these  global
       nets.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the applyGlobalNets command usage.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man applyGlobalNets

Related Information
       Power Planning and Routing chapter in the Innovus User Guide.

